articles.title: Trans influencer Dylan Mulvaney says 'It's hard to see the light now' - Daily Mail
articles.description: Trans influencer Dylan Mulvaney has broken her silence saying 'it's hard to see the light now' after 'the week I've been having' hitting back at critics after receiving backlash for her Nike bra deal.
